The paper presents a novel attitude control law for multicopters, which is a topic related to robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the safety perspective of the controller, which is related to control systems (cs.SY). The paper uses a Lyapunov function to prove stability, which is a common technique in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also presents experimental validation, which may involve computer vision techniques (cs.CV).
